<p><lb/>Vir Excellentissime et Doctissime.</p>
<p>Accepi<del> ultimam</del> Tuam <rs key="B_1716-06-19_991170517050905501" type="letter">epistolam</rs> <choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>die</expan></choice> <date when="1716-06-19">19. Junii</date> scriptam, qua me certiorem facere
 <lb/>dignatus es, me brevi ab <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>.</abbr> <abbr>Dnis</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858 pers_DE-588-1253768439 pers_DE-588-1178380696" type="persons">Moderatoribus</rs> Serenissimo <rs type="organisation">Senatui</rs>
<lb/>propositum iri, quod gratum fuit intelligere; Vehementer etenim desidero, ut
         <lb/>res h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c cito plenum sortiatur exitum, siquidem <subst><del>ante fa</del><add>post</add></subst> confirmat<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> demum
         <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="organisation">Serenissimo Senatu</rs> election<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <note type="editorial">Hier hat der Autor eine Wortumstellung vorgenommen</note>et transmissam vocationem secure me ad iter
         <lb/>instruere queam. Expecto itaque in singulos dies solennem istam vocationem.
         <lb/>Tuumque circa ulterius <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me facienda consilium, <del>quod ibi <gap/><unclear>partiturum</unclear></del>
<lb/><del>esse tam</del>quo me non leviter adjutum iri gaudeo. Interim quas in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cedentibus
         <lb/>meis <rs key="B_1716-06-06_991170517051105501" type="letter">Literis</rs> <choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>die</expan></choice> <date when="1716-06-06">6. Junii</date> scriptis Tibi egi gratias pro continuis Tuis et
         <lb/>indefessis in hoc negotio laboribus, denuo repeto meque ob eximium Tuum
         <lb/>erga me favorem insigniter<del> me</del> Tibi devinctum et ad omnis generis officia,
         <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quidem <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me proficisci poterunt, Tibi <add>vicissim</add> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>standa obligatum esse,
         <lb/>lubens agnosco.</p>
<p><lb/>Conscribam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> notanda habeo in <rs type="biblio">solutione</rs><!-- bibliotag --> <add><rs type="biblio">Problematis</rs><!-- bibliotag --> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me propositi</add> quam <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1156361761" type="person">Checozzi</rs> dedit,
          <lb/><add>eaque</add> proxime<del>que</del> transmittam inserenda <rs type="keyword">Diario Veneto</rs> sub meo vel <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Adgnati</rs>
<lb/>mei nomine. Theorema <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtono</rs> in <rs key="biblio_KGWAEINJ" type="biblio"><choice><orig>optica</orig><reg>Optica</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>pag.</abbr> 231<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> suppositum, et
         <lb/>cujus demonstrationem petis, paulo obscurius ibidem enunciatum est,
         <lb/>en illud clarioribus verbis <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me conceptum: Si duo corpora <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualia <formula>A</formula> et <formula>a</formula>
<lb/>cad<subst><del>ent deorsum</del><add>ere incipiant</add></subst> ex punctis <del>quietis</del> <formula>A</formula> et <formula>a</formula>,<del>tr</del> et<del> virib</del> perpendi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>culariter deorsum urgeantur<add> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></add> viribus quibuscunque<del> in<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></del> perpe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tuo quidem variabilibus sed in singulis ab initio casus <formula>A</formula> et <formula>a</formula> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qua<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>libus distantiis <formula>B</formula>, <formula>b</formula>, datam et constantem ad se invicem rationem
          <pb facs="1038348" n="140r"/>
<lb/>habentibus, erunt motus per <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualia spatia <formula>AB</formula>, <formula>ab</formula>,<del> diver</del> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> diversis istis viribus
         <lb/>generati,<subst><del> id est</del><add> seu</add></subst> velocitates in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualibus <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> punctis <formula>A</formula>, <formula>a</formula>, distantiis acquisit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/>in ratione subduplicata earundem virium: Quam propositionem ego sic de<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>monstro: <subst><del>Sint</del><add>Vocentur</add></subst> velocitates in punctis <formula>B</formula> et <formula>b</formula> acquisit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>V</formula> et <formula>u</formula>, tempora quibus spatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>la<del> pro</del> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualia et infinite parva <formula>BC</formula> et <formula>bc</formula>, percurruntur <formula>T</formula> et <formula>t</formula>, et<del> vires</del> ratio data
         <lb/>virium <add>sit</add> ut <formula>F</formula> ad <formula>f</formula>,<del> erit</del> erunt propter spatiola <formula>BC</formula>, <formula>bc</formula> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualia, tempora quibus h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> spatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>la percurruntur velocitatibus reciproce proportionalia <abbr>i. e.</abbr> <formula>T.t::u.V</formula><note type="editorial">Moderne Schreibweise: <formula>T:t=u:V</formula></note>, sed
         <lb/>incrementa velocitatum casu per <formula>BC</formula>, <formula>bc</formula> acquisita sunt in composita ratione
          <lb/><subst><del>virium et</del><add>directa dictor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></add></subst> temporum et virium in <formula>B</formula>et <formula>b</formula> agentium <abbr>i. e.</abbr> <formula>dV.du::FT.ft::</formula> (per modo
          <lb/>dicta) <formula>Fu.fV</formula> ,<note type="editorial">Das letzte F in der Formel wurde von einer Majuskel zu einer Minuskel korrigiert</note> ergo multiplicando extrema et media <formula>fVdV = Fudu</formula>, et
         <lb/>integrando <formula>\frac{1}{2}fVV=\frac{1}{2}Fuu</formula> <note type="editorial">In der Formel wurde VV zu uu korrigiert.</note>sive <formula>fVV=Fuu</formula> et<del> pr</del> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualitate in proportionem
         <lb/>resoluta <formula>VV.uu::F.f</formula> id est quadrata velocitatum<del> ut</del> sunt ut vires. <abbr>q. e. d.</abbr>
<lb/>Idem etiam i<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ediate confici potest ex <abbr>Prop.</abbr> 39<choice><orig><choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice></orig><reg>,</reg></choice> <rs key="biblio_73DJ8AIG" type="biblio">Lib. 1<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> <abbr>Princ.</abbr> <abbr>Phil. Nat.</abbr></rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtoni</rs>,
         <lb/>ibi enim demonstratum est<del> vires</del> velocitate<subst><del>s</del><add>m</add></subst> in loco quovis E<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> (<abbr>vid. Fig. Newt.</abbr>)
         <lb/>esse ut are<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> curviline<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>ABGE</formula> latus quadratum, jam quia singul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> applicat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/><formula>DE</formula> dictam aream <formula>ABGE</formula> complentes denotant vires, et h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vires semper
         <lb/>eandem inter se habe<del>a</del>nt rationem, erunt etiam omnes applicat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>DE</formula> simul
         <lb/>sumt<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> id est tota area <formula>ABGE</formula> in eadem ratione virium, unde consequitur velo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>citates esse ut latus quadratum earundum virium.</p><closer><salute>Quod superest Vale et <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Adgna<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>to</rs> meo <choice><abbr>pl.</abbr><expan>plurimam</expan></choice> salutem meo nomine dicere ne graveris.</salute> <dateline><abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1716-07-04">4. Julij 1716</date>.</dateline></closer>
